EVALUATE
  ROW(
  "Commercial", 'Navigation Buttons'[Commercial]
)

EVALUATE
  ROW(
  "ITC_Volumes", 'Navigation Buttons'[ITC Volumes]
)

EVALUATE
  ROW(
  "Absentees___Refunds", 'Navigation Buttons'[Absentees & Refunds]
)

EVALUATE
  ROW(
  "PB_IELTS_vs_CD_IELTS", 'Navigation Buttons'[PB IELTS vs CD IELTS]
)

DEFINE VAR __DS0FilterTable = 
  TREATAS({"ITC Volumes"}, 'Data Plan'[Report])

EVALUATE
  SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
    __DS0FilterTable,
    "MinLast_Updated", IGNORE(CALCULATE(MIN('Data Plan'[Last Updated])))
  )

EVALUATE
  ROW(
  "YoY_Change____", 'IELTS PB&CD Hist&Fcast Volumes'[YoY Change (%)]
)

EVALUATE
  ROW(
    "YoY_Change____", 'IELTS PB&CD Hist&Fcast Volumes'[YoY Change (%)],
    "IELTS_KPI_Arrows", 'IELTS PB&CD Hist&Fcast Volumes'[IELTS KPI Arrows]
  )

DEFINE
  VAR __DS0FilterTable = 
    TREATAS({"20-21",
      "21-22",
      "22-23",
      "19-20"}, 'FY Order'[Financial Year])

  VAR __DS0Core = 
    SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
      'FY Order'[Financial Year],
      'IELTS PB&CD Hist&Fcast Volumes'[IOC or IOP],
      __DS0FilterTable,
      "Sum_of_Vol", 'IELTS PB&CD Hist&Fcast Volumes'[Sum of Vol]
    )

  VAR __DS0PrimaryWindowed = 
    TOPN(201, SUMMARIZE(__DS0Core, 'FY Order'[Financial Year]), 'FY Order'[Financial Year], 1)

  VAR __DS0SecondaryBase = 
    SUMMARIZE(__DS0Core, 'IELTS PB&CD Hist&Fcast Volumes'[IOC or IOP])

  VAR __DS0Secondary = 
    TOPN(62, __DS0SecondaryBase, 'IELTS PB&CD Hist&Fcast Volumes'[IOC or IOP], 1)

  VAR __DS0BodyLimited = 
    NATURALLEFTOUTERJOIN(
      __DS0PrimaryWindowed,
      SUBSTITUTEWITHINDEX(
        __DS0Core,
        "ColumnIndex",
        __DS0Secondary,
        'IELTS PB&CD Hist&Fcast Volumes'[IOC or IOP],
        ASC
      )
    )

EVALUATE
  __DS0Secondary

ORDER BY
  'IELTS PB&CD Hist&Fcast Volumes'[IOC or IOP]

EVALUATE
  __DS0BodyLimited

ORDER BY
  'FY Order'[Financial Year], [ColumnIndex]

DEFINE
  VAR __DS0Core = 
    SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
      'Calendar'[Month],
      'Calendar'[MonthNum],
      "Sum_of_Vol__21_22_", 'IELTS PB&CD Hist&Fcast Volumes'[Sum of Vol (21/22)],
      "Sum_of_Vol_Actuals__22_23_", 'IELTS PB&CD Hist&Fcast Volumes'[Sum of Vol Actuals (22/23)],
      "Sum_of_Vol_FC___Actuals_22_23_", 'IELTS PB&CD Hist&Fcast Volumes'[Sum of Vol FC & Actuals(22/23)]
    )

  VAR __DS0PrimaryWindowed = 
    TOPN(1001, __DS0Core, 'Calendar'[MonthNum], 1, 'Calendar'[Month], 1)

EVALUATE
  __DS0PrimaryWindowed

ORDER BY
  'Calendar'[MonthNum], 'Calendar'[Month]

EVALUATE

    TREATAS({"20-21",
      "21-22",
      "22-23",
      "19-20"}, 'FY Order'[Financial Year])

  VAR __DS0FilterTable2 = 
    TREATAS({"DCU (Primary)"}, 'IELTS PB&CD Hist&Fcast Volumes'[Centre])

  VAR __DS0Core = 
    SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
      'FY Order'[Financial Year],
      'IELTS PB&CD Hist&Fcast Volumes'[IOC or IOP],
      __DS0FilterTable,
      __DS0FilterTable2,
      "Sum_of_Vol", 'IELTS PB&CD Hist&Fcast Volumes'[Sum of Vol]
    )

  VAR __DS0PrimaryWindowed = 
    TOPN(201, SUMMARIZE(__DS0Core, 'FY Order'[Financial Year]), 'FY Order'[Financial Year], 1)

  VAR __DS0SecondaryBase = 
    SUMMARIZE(__DS0Core, 'IELTS PB&CD Hist&Fcast Volumes'[IOC or IOP])

  VAR __DS0Secondary = 
    TOPN(62, __DS0SecondaryBase, 'IELTS PB&CD Hist&Fcast Volumes'[IOC or IOP], 1)

  VAR __DS0BodyLimited = 
    NATURALLEFTOUTERJOIN(
      __DS0PrimaryWindowed,
      SUBSTITUTEWITHINDEX(
        __DS0Core,
        "ColumnIndex",
        __DS0Secondary,
        'IELTS PB&CD Hist&Fcast Volumes'[IOC or IOP],
        ASC
      )
    )

EVALUATE
  __DS0Secondary

ORDER BY
  'IELTS PB&CD Hist&Fcast Volumes'[IOC or IOP]

EVALUATE
  __DS0BodyLimited

ORDER BY
  'FY Order'[Financial Year], [ColumnIndex]

  VAR __ValueFilterDM0 = 
    FILTER(

          __DS0FilterTable,
